Rucder
======

= install =
 ruby script/plugin install http://asyrinx.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/rails/examples/rucder_example/vendor/plugins/rucder


= db:migrate =
generate migration for rucder

 ruby script/generate migration create_rucder_tables

and copy following:
----------------------------
